body:
![AMS' Crop Sweeper Enchantment](https://i.postimg.cc/T3bR6j4q/MUTE-Title-2.png)

**AMS' Crop Sweeper Enchantment** mod introduces a powerful new enchantment for hoes, allowing players to efficiently harvest fully grown crops within a specific radius and automatically replanting them. With this enchantment, you can quickly clear large fields of crops with a single action, making farming faster and more convenient.

![Enchantment](https://i.postimg.cc/fTDXkKdC/Enchanting-Table.png) 
![Base feature](https://i.postimg.cc/9Qbg9GK0/chrome-capture-2024-9-4.gif) 

### Features
**Enchantment Levels**
  - **Crop Sweeper I** Harvests fully grown crops in a 1-block radius around the targeted crop and replants seeds (min level 10);
  - **Crop Sweeper II** Expands the harvesting radius to 2 blocks (min level 20);
  - **Crop Sweeper III** Expands the harvesting radius to 3 blocks (min level 30);


**Vertical Harvesting**
  - Vertical blocks within a y-level of 1 are also harvested;

**Selective Harvesting**
  - Only crops of the same type as the initially targeted crop will be harvested, ensuring your fields stay organized;

**Compatibility**
  - Tested with popular mods such as Farmer's Delight;
  - Fully compatible with other crop mods;

*Note: Replanting feature is only available for versions 2.0.0+*

